[W] Tapu Storm GX
Shuffle your opponent's Active Pokemon and all cards attached to it into their deck. If your opponent has no Benched Pokemon, this attack does nothing. (You can't use more than 1 GX attack in a game.)

extendedData.name: CardText
extendedData.value:
Ability — Aero Trail
When you play this Pokemon from your hand onto your Bench during your turn, you may move any number of Lightning Energy from your other Pokemon to this Pokemon. If you do, switch this Pokemon with your Active Pokemon.

extendedData.name: Attack 2
extendedData.value:
[1LL] Tapu Thunder GX (50x)
This attack does 50 damage times the amount of Energy attached to all of your opponent's Pokemon. (You can't use more than 1 GX attack in a game.)

extendedData.name: CardText
extendedData.value:
Ability — Wonder Tag
When you play this Pokemon from your hand onto your Bench during your turn, you may search your deck for a Supporter card, reveal it, and put it into your hand. Then, shuffle your deck.
